                     <interp inst="t18320906-264-person2164" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a Policeman. I saw the prisoner's hand in Mr. Roe's pocket - I had seen him attempt a gentleman's pocket before, and watched him; a person came in between us, and I did not see him take Mr. Roe's handkerchief out - Mr. Roe turned round to catch hold of him; he ran away; I pursued, and overtook him in Brooke-street; he said he was going to school, and not to pick pockets; but I had seen him attempt more than one pocket before - I found nothing on him.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I did not take it.</p>

               <p>GUILTY. Aged 9.</p>
